https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-jshint

----- jshint -----
Faz validações em arquivos js. Verifica a qualidade do código, como falta de ; por exemplo.

npm install grunt-contrib-jshint --save-dev  //instala o plugin
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-jshint');  //no arquivio gruntfile.js


----- concat -----
https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-concat
Concatena arquivos js.

npm install grunt-contrib-concat --save-dev
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-concat');


----- uglify -----
https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-uglify
Minificar todos os arquivos js já concatenados em um arquivo único.

npm install grunt-contrib-uglify --save-dev
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-uglify');


----- cssmin -----
https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-cssmin
Minificar arquivos css.
npm install grunt-contrib-cssmin --save-dev
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-cssmin');


----- htmlmin -----
https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-htmlmin
Minificar html

npm install grunt-contrib-htmlmin --save-dev
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-htmlmin');


----- clean -----
Deletar arquivos gerados no processo de build
https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-clean

npm install grunt-contrib-clean --save-dev
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-clean');

----- copy -----
Copiar arquivos e renomear arquivos.
https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-contrib-copy

npm install grunt-contrib-copy --save-dev
grunt.loadNpmTasks('grunt-contrib-copy');




